Date: 1995-06-21

Title: Exact Results for the Supersymmetric $G_2$ Gauge Theories

Comments: LaTex, 15 pages

Journal-ref: Mod. Phys. Lett. A10 (1995) 1871

We study the $N=1$ supersymmetric $G_2$ gauge theories with $N_f$ flavors ofquarks in the fundamental vector representation. We find dynamically generatedsuperpotentials, smooth quantum moduli space, quantum moduli space withadditional mesons, non trivial IR fixed points.